    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for someone looking for a functional car with a few cosmetic and mechanical needs. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. While it runs and drives well, it may require some minor maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition. It's a solid choice for a daily driver if you don't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
