    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a standard of care that is exceedingly rare. Mechanically impeccable and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning enthusiast. We invite you to inspect this benchmark of quality firsthand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
